Dr Maya is extremely professional yet friendly 
She always explains about the treatment before starting treatment in terms of setting expectations 
During treatment while we are wondering what’s happening she provides timely updates 
I along with my family always goes to Dr Vora Dental Clinic at Mulund and Dr Maya is always one of the most favourite Doctor that we book the appointment 
Sometimes it’s challenging to get her appointment as all the appointments are always gets booked but that tells us how professional she is and that’s why everyone prefers booking her appointment 

Thanks a Lot Dr Maya

Dr Maya Nair is well competent in her job. She has the patience to deal with customers which is very paramount. Without asking her for any details she voluntarily discussed and explained overall hygiene to be maintained, how to brush the teeth etc. Small details but very important.
She encouraged and gave me the courage to continue with the treatment quote “ Don’t get scared it is normal we are all there for you” . Very happy with her confident at the same time concern and care . 👍😊💯

Dr.Maya Nair in my view is one of those Doctor who press for perfection tirelessly with great patience & focus. In recent time its a rare quality. Her attitude towards her profession is admirable.

For a person visiting a dentist after 20 years the idea of RCT is terrifying but thanks to Doc for explaining every bit of the procedure which clears the mental block & make you feel relax. Needless to say the procedure was done painlessly & without any discomfort. 

Thanks a lot for the  efforts taken & would certainly recommend her.

Thanks
